DISCLAIMER FOR BLOCKCHAIN USAGE:

This software is for educational purposes and testing only.

1. SECURITY:
   - This code has not been professionally audited
   - Do not use on mainnet with real funds
   - Test thoroughly on local network first
   - Use only with small test amounts on testnets

2. TESTNET DEPLOYMENT:
   - Never share your private key
   - Never commit .env file to version control
   - Testnet tokens have no real value
   - Use only accounts you own

3. PRODUCTION USAGE:
   - Have the code professionally audited
   - Test extensively on all networks
   - Use secure key management
   - Maintain proper documentation

4. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY:
   - Authors assume no liability
   - Use at your own risk
   - Blockchain transactions are irreversible
   - Always verify contract actions

